FBIS3-16403 "drsov051_p_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-051 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Draftees To Serve in Russian Border Troops NC1503193694 Yerevan SNARK in English 1257 GMT 15 Mar 94 NC1503193694 Yerevan SNARK Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Yerevan, March 15 (SNARK)--Armenian draftees will henceforth serve in Russian Frontier Troops, located in Armenia. Such agreement has been signed today in Yerevan by Russian Frontier Troops' commander Andrey Nikolayev and Armenian State Minister for Defence Vazgen Sargisyan. General-lieutenant Nikolayev has also met with Armenian Vice-President Gagik Arutyunyan and Prime Minister Grant Bagratyan.
